Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.00,0:01:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.65,0:01:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Queen to F3.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.05,0:01:35.37,TEXT-JP EPSON 太明朝体Ｂ-ja,,0,0,0,,f3　クイーン
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.32,0:01:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
